           if        w-cnt-prn-flg-int    not  = spaces
                     go to prn-rou-pri-891.
           perform   prn-fin-cic-000      thru prn-fin-cic-999        .
       prn-rou-pri-891.
           exit.
       prn-rou-pri-900.
